name: Looking at the river #2
description: Abstract glitch art made with AnaCam and Vaporgram on the good old HTC Incredible S with custom unofficial CyanogenMod 11 firmware (Android 4.4.4. KitKat). Based on a photo of the Tysmenytsia River taken from the pedestrian bridge on the HTC Incredible S with AnaCam (available at f-droid.org), additional effects were applied using the standard gallery app and Vaporgram (available in the Play Market). 1125x1500 px. Author: Mkriiis.
